==French==

===Relative pronoun===
'''lesquels''' ''mpl''
# ''plural of [[lequel]]''; (following a preposition) which, that, whom
#:''Elle préfère les hommes avec '''lequels''' tu sortais.''
#:"She prefers the men with '''whom''' you you were going out."
#:''Il se remet à travailler sur les projet pour '''lequels''' il avait déjà passé tellement de temps.''
#:"He's starting to work on the projects on '''which''' he had already spent so much time."

====Related terms====
*[[auxquels]] ([[à]] + lesquels)
*[[desquels]] ([[de#French|de]] + lesquels)

===Interrogative pronoun===
'''lequels''' ''mpl''
# [[which]] ones
#:''Passe-moi les ballons. - '''Lequels''' ? Il y en a cinq.''
#:"Pass me the balls. - '''Which ones'''? There are five."

